  EffectDiscription_ENG: "\uFF1CRush\uFF1E.\n\uFF1CSecurity A. +1\uFF1E \n[On Play]
    [When Digivolving] You may place 1 level 4 or lower [DM]\_trait Digimon card
    from your trash as this Digimon's top digivolution card. Then, delete 1 of your
    opponent's Digimon with the same color as any of this Digimon's digivolution
    cards. If this Digimon has 6 or more colors in its digivolution cards, instead
    delete 1 of each of your opponent's Digimon with different colors.\n[All Turns]
    This Digimon gets +1000 DP for each color in its digivolution cards."
